added.title: The Sunflower
added.description: Our Trio makes a new friend in the Creek, but when her pet befalls a tragic fate, Kelsey believes she knows how to help.

added.title: Craig World
added.description: Craig creates an amusement park in the Creek! But when things start to get stale, he vows to make it bigger and better, no matter what it takes!

added.title: Mother of All Cards
added.description: Chef attempts to trick the kids into making his mother gifts after he forgets Mother's Day.

added.title: Duncan Disorderly
added.description: Duncan escapes during a community walk only to discover he has to babysit Cody and Bridgette.

added.title: Soother or Later
added.description: A terrified Duncan, who's afraid of lightning, learns it's even harder to break back into school than it was to break out when he finally escapes and finds himself in a dark alley with Izzy during a thunderstorm.

added.title: Wasted True Potential
added.description: In the wake of the previous season's victory, the ninja have gone soft and Master Wu must remind them of who they truly are.

added.title: Questing For Quests
added.description: Realizing they have gone soft, the ninja search for a quest to reignite their Spinjitzu training. Unfortunately, NINJAGO City is enjoying a period of rare tranquility.

added.title: A Rocky Start
added.description: The ninja have found their quest! Now they just have to get there, which involves a road trip through the Desert of Doom, a region supposedly inhabited by a giant scarab beetle.

added.title: Once and for All
added.description: Nya, Jay, Cole and Kai face off against the Ice Emperor's dreaded dragon, while Lloyd and his newfound allies, Kataru and Grimfax, confront the Ice Emperor himself.

added.title: Awakenings
added.description: The dramatic conclusion of the Never-Realm saga, in which old friends are reunited and the power of friendship is pitted against the corrupting power of the Scroll of Forbidden Spinjitzu.

added.title: #DinnerForFive
added.description: Barbara Gordon finds herself in a tight spot when an awkward dinner with a new friend's father turns into something so much more.

added.title: #LivingTheNightmare
added.description: When Zee's friends are held captive in their nightmares by a dream demon, she'll have to confront her own hidden insecurities, or risk the Super Hero Girls being trapped in a prison of their own fears forever.

added.title: #AllAboutZee
added.description: Zee Zatara is flattered when she meets an overeager admirer named Casey Krinsky, but soon realizes that "her biggest fan" wants much more than just an autograph.

added.title: #TweenTitans
added.description: Jessica Cruz is hired by billionaire playboy Bruce Wayne to chaperone young Dick Grayson's Metropolis birthday bash and brings Karen Beecher along to help, but the girls get more than they bargained for when the TWEEN party guests reveal their TITANic personalities.

added.title: #EmperorPenguin
added.description: When Barbara Gordon attempts to do something nice for a friend, she ends up in the clutches of the Penguin, a high school mob boss who blackmails her into an increasingly desperate situation from which only Batgirl can save her.

added.title: Plundsmas
added.description:
The Mutants refuse to celebrate their favorite holiday, Plunds-Mas, now that Plun-Darr is gone. So now it's up to the Thundercats to raise their spirits by enacting the
eight horrors of Plunds-Mas!

added.title: Killing Time
added.description: Mumm-Ra, the Ever-Living decides he'll nap for a thousand years, till the Thundercats are long gone. But when he wakes up, he's shocked to discover that Third Earth is even more in love with them than ever.

added.title: Grune
added.description: The ThunderCats face the greatest threat of their lives: Grune the Destroyer! He's the ghost of an evil ThunderCat and he wants revenge! How are They Gonna Beat Grune??? You'll have to watch the episode!

added.title: The First Thundsgiving
added.description: Tygra is furious after the other Thundercats eat the last of his Thunderian ingredients. To make it up to him they go hunting for substitutes on Third Earth to show him the food on their new planet is just as delicious as the food they had back on their old home.

added.title: Mandora Saves Christmas
added.description: Santa Claus is on the run from Mandora! Can the Thundercats help him get off Third Earth without getting caught? And can Santa Claus teach them a little something about this weird new holiday "Christmas"?

added.title: Green with Envy
added.description: When the local news interviews Uncle Andrew about his toy inventing, an envious Galileo stages a play in the park with the help of Axel and the team, only to be interrupted by an equally envious Madcap - out to steal the spotlight for himself!

added.title: Bring on the Bad Guys
added.description: Axel, Zoe, and the team confront Madcap and his minions as they terrorize a local supermarket.

added.title: Spies Like Us
added.description: Uncle Andrew warns Axel that his vintage "Agent Danger" action figure is off-limits, only to have the toy escape on its own! Axel and the team must return Danger to its rightful place before Uncle Andrew finds out.

added.title: Return of Thermometron 9000
added.description: During a brutal heatwave, Axel and his team must track down Thermometron 9000, stolen by Ice Crusher for two purposes - to keep his hockey rink from melting and to bait the good toys into a rematch!

added.title: Just Like Robots
added.description: Axel and the team find themselves bested by Madcap when the baddie uses their digital devices to track their every move in combat, forcing our heroes to act unpredictably.

added.title: The AB Bakugan Battle League!
added.description: With all the mayhem and destruction Haavik is causing, the Awesome Brawlers decide that a bit of Bakugan brawling is the perfect distraction to take their minds off all the trouble. With the help of some friends, they start the Awesome Brawler Bakugan Battle league!/ The Awesome Brawler's Bakugan Battle league rages on. Just as the semifinal round comes to a close, an uninvited guest crashes the party, bringing an alarming end to the battle league.

added.title: Haavik's Challenge/Storm Haavik's Tower
added.description: Haavik's Challenge: Haavik has crashed the Awesome Brawlers Bakugan League, and challenges the Awesome Brawlers in a battle league of his own!/ Storm Haavik's Tower: In order to keep Earth and Vestroia safe and rescue Drago, the Awesome Brawlers agree to enter Haavik's Bakugan Battle League, and race toward Haavik's tower for the final showdown.

added.title: High Flying Hostiles/Backfire Brawl
added.description: High Flying Hostiles: While escorting the Mind Core Cell to AAAnimus Campus, the AO are attacked by Masato Kazami and his Body Guards./Backfire Brawl: Philomena's attempt to refocus the Mind Core Cell's power backfires and the AO must fight their fellow employees inside the AAAnimus Campus.

added.title: Hostile Take Over/The Big Bounce
added.description: Hostile Take Over: After more unsuccessful attempts to harness Core Cell energy the AO must battle their own Bakugan with AAAnimus tech in order to save them./The Big Bounce: The AO confront Philomena with concerns about her control over the Core Cell energy and are fired in the most unceremonious of manners.

added.title: Awesome vs. AAAnimus
added.description: Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 1: The AO plan on sneaking into AAAnimus and rescuing their Bakugan but are stopped by Benton who offers up an alternate plan./Awesome V Aaanimus, Part 2: The AO team up with Benton Dusk to recapture their stolen Bakugan and free the energy from the Mind Core Cell under the control of AAAnimus.

added.title: Videodrone
added.description: Mega Man must stop Hypno Woman from turning the students and teachers at Silicon Central into her mindless drones.

added.title: Please Rush Home
added.description: A misunderstanding between Mega Man and Rush ends in the robo-pup running away from home, only to be reunited and reconciled during a confrontation with Wave Man.

added.title: Blaze of Glory
added.description: Mega Man and Suna must overcome a sibling dispute over what to do on their day off in order to stop Fire Man from overheating the city.

added.title: Nice on Ice
added.description: An "unscheduled" TV appearance not only lands Aki in hot water for missing class, but sets Ice Man on a misguided mission to "unite" (i.e. freeze together) every human and robot couple in the city!

added.title: Hard Times in Silicon City
added.description: Mega Man must stop Blasto Woman from plundering the Museum of the Hard Age and its cache of military grade weaponry.

added.title: Two Lies, One Truth
added.description: As Lloyd unmasks Mystake for who she truly is, Emperor Garmadon embraces Harumi as his daughter of darkness. Meanwhile, Wu holds onto faith as he leads his friends into dangerous Oni territory in the hope of finding Firstbourne's nest

added.title: The Weakest Link
added.description: Lloyd turns the tables on Harumi to take his father's power away, and the Ninja learn what it takes to be a Dragon Hunter.

added.title: Saving Faith
added.description: Lloyd and his team plot to take control of the Oni Titan. Meanwhile in the First Realm, the Ninja fall into Iron Baron's clutches and an old master returns.

added.title: Lessons for a Master
added.description: When Iron Baron forces Wu to retrieve the Dragon Armor, things don't go as planned. In Ninjago, Lloyd can only endure so much as he holds onto hope for the Ninjas' return.

added.title: Green Destiny
added.description: The Ninja finally return home and unite to stop Emperor Garmadon, forcing Lloyd to make a decision that will forever change Ninjago.

added.title: Dos mentiras una verdad
added.description: Cuando Lloyd desenmascara y revela la identidad de Mystake, el Emperador Garmadon acepta a Harumi como su hija de la oscuridad. Mientras tanto, Wu se aferra a su fe al llevar a sus amigos hacia territorios Oni peligrosos esperando encontrar el nido de la Primogénita.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: El eslabon mas debil
added.description: Lloyd le paga con la misma moneda a Harumi para quitarle el poder a su padre, y los Ninjas aprenden lo que se necesita para ser un Cazador de Dragones.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Salvando a Faith
added.description: Lloyd y su equipo planean tomar el control del Oni Titan. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, los Ninja caen en las garras del Barón de Hierro y un viejo maestro regresa.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Lecciones para un maestro
added.description: Cuando el Barón de Hierro obliga a Wu a tomar la Armadura de Dragón, las cosas no salen como se planearon. En Ninjago, hay un límite de lo que Lloyd puede soportar mientras se aferra a la esperanza del regreso de los Ninjas.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Destino verde
added.description: Los Ninjas regresan por fin a casa y se unen para detener al Emperador Garmadon, obligando a Lloyd a tomar una decisión que cambiará por siempre a Ninjago.
added.originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

added.title: Potencial Desperdiciado
added.description: A raíz de la victoria de la temporada anterior, los ninjas se han ablandado y el Maestro Wu debe recordarles quiénes son realmente.

added.title: Buscando Misiones
added.description: Al darse cuenta de que se han ablandado, el ninja busca una misión para reactivar su entrenamiento de Spinjitzu. Desafortunadamente, la ciudad de NINJAGO está disfrutando de un período de rara tranquilidad.

added.title: Un Comienzo Dificil
added.description: iLos ninja han encontrado su búsqueda! Ahora solo tienen que llegar allí, lo que implica un viaje por carretera a través del desierto de Doom, una región supuestamente habitada por un escarabajo gigante.

added.title: Enemigos en el Aire
added.description: Cuando Los Fantásticos transportan la Célula Núcleo a las instalaciones de AAAnimus, son atacados por Masato Kazami y sus Guardaespaldas.

added.title: Un Experimento Fallido
added.description: El plan de Filomena Dusk para redireccionar la energía de la Célula Núcleo fracasa, y Los Fantásticos deben pelear contra sus propios compañeros de trabajo dentro de las instalaciones de AAAnimus.

added.title: Perdiendo el Control
added.description: Después de más intentos fallidos por aprovechar la energía la Célula núcleo, Los Fantásticos deben pelear contra sus propios Bakugan usando tecnología AAAnimus para salvarlos.

added.title: Despedidos
added.description: Los Fantásticos confrontan a Filomena, preocupados de que ella controle la energía de la Célula núcleo, y son despedidos de una forma poco profesional.

added.title: Fantasticos vs. AAAnimus Parte 1
added.description: Los Fantásticos planean infiltrarse a AAAnimus para rescatar a sus Bakugan, pero Benton los detiene para ofrecerles un plan alternativo.

added.title: Fantasticos vs. AAAnimus Parte 2
added.description: Los Fantásticos unen fuerzas con Benton Dusk para rescatar a sus Bakugan y liberar la energía de la Célula Núcleo que AAAnimus tiene bajo su control.

added.title: #CenaParaCinco
added.description: Barbara Gordon está en apuros cuando una cena incómoda el padre de una nueva amiga, se convierte en algo muy diferente.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Que Vengan Los Chicos Malos
added.description: Axel, Zoe y el equipo se enfrentan a Madcap y sus secuaces mientras aterrorizan a un supermercado local.

added.title: Duncan liberado
added.description: Duncan se escapa durante un paseo en la comunidad solo para descubrir que tiene que cuidar a Cody y Bridgette.

added.title: Espias Como Nosotros
added.description: El tío Andrew le advierte a Axel que su figura de acción "Agente Peligro" está prohibida, isolo para que el juguete escape solo! Axel y el equipo deben devolver a Danger al lugar que le corresponde antes de que el tío Andrew se entere.

added.title: Un Dragon en la Guarderia
added.description: Duncan finalmente logra escapar solo para descubrir que ha olvidado su chupete y necesita entrar a la escuela para recuperarlo.

added.title: El regreso de Thermometron 9000
added.description: Durante una ola de calor brutal, Axel y su equipo deben rastrear Thermometron 9000, robado por Ice Crusher para dos propósitos: ievitar que su pista de hockey se derrita y cebar los buenos juguetes en una revancha!

added.title: De Una Vez por Todas
added.description: Nya, Jay, Cole y Kai se enfrentan al temido dragón del Emperador de Hielo, mientras Lloyd y sus nuevos aliados, Kataru y Grimfax se enfrentan al Emperador en persona.

added.title: Despertares
added.description: Esta es la dramática conclusión de la saga del Reino del Jamás, en la que viejos amigos se reúnen y el poder de la amistad se enfrenta al poder oscuro del Pergamino del Spinjitzu Prohibido.

added.title: Como Robots
added.description: Axel y el equipo se ven superados por Madcap cuando el malo usa sus dispositivos digitales para rastrear cada uno de sus movimientos en combate, lo que obliga a nuestros héroes a actuar de manera impredecible.
